{"tid":1568780,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"網上買香水","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:32:01.000Z","uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3bed0408ffb3cecbfc5d119798fd6b768bcd601","tid":1568780,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"小弟住墨爾本，用男性香水都用左一段時間，平時一直都係去Myer買<br />\n唔太敢去chemist warehouse買因為個價錢通常都平幾十percent，好怕係假貨或者廠商劣質貨<br />\n最近見到一個網站叫fragranceX賣香水更加低價，上網check左下正面同負面評論都唔少<br />\n<br />\n求問下有無巴絲係行內人可以話我知chemist warehouse或fragranceX點解會賣咁平？<br />\nFragranceX我唔知，但Chemist warehouse響澳洲做到咁大，我唔信佢地會賣假貨，會唔會係廠商派劣等貨？<br />\n<br />\n覺得Myer賣得好貴，但同時又唔希望比錢買左假貨或劣等貨<br />\n連登有無人做呢行可以解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793be07fc0e88e5a4cf01101fe037101af5266ae","tid":1568780,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:30:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b424598f9f8971cd81536381b97a9aaa9e5d4dee","tid":1568780,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}